name: CCSBusTracker
0:
”Alexa ask CCS Bus Tracker about 316”
”Open CCS Bus Tracker and where is my bus 316”
”Ask CCS Bus Tracker if my bus 316 on time”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: c. c. s. bus tracker
des: Based on the bus number mentioned by the user, this skill checks the Twitter handle @CCSBuses. The Twitter API would return a tweet for the mentioned bus number if available. If it has been tweeted between yesterday and time when skill is invoked and if it is not a retweet then it is conveyed to the user.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
